---
<BaseLayout
  title="Discover Philippines ‚Äî Travel Guides by Scott & Jenice"
  description="Your immersive guide to the Philippine islands ‚Äî cinematic video, local tips, and honest recommendations from 23 years of travel."
>
  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO ‚Äî 100vh cinematic with video background
       ============================================================ -->
  <header class="hp-hero">
    <video
      class="hp-hero-video"
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      preload="metadata"
    >
      <source src="/videos/destinations/boracay-hero-full.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
    </video>
    <div class="hp-hero-gradient" />
    <div class="hp-hero-overlay" />
    <div class="hp-hero-noise" />

    <div class="hp-hero-content">
      <h1 class="hp-hero-title">The Philippines Through Our Eyes</h1>
      <p class="hp-hero-subtitle">We're Scott and Jenice ‚Äî an American planner and his Filipina wife from Pampanga. These are the islands we keep coming back to, the food we actually eat, and the prices we actually paid.</p>
      <div class="hp-hero-actions">
        <a href="#map" class="hp-btn hp-btn--primary">Explore the Map</a>
        <a href="/plan/" class="hp-btn hp-btn--secondary">Plan Your Trip</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hp-scroll-hint">Scroll<br />&#8595;</div>
  </header>

  <!-- ============================================================
       TRUST BAR ‚Äî Stats strip
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="hp-trust-bar">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="hp-trust-stats">
        <a href="/about/scott/" class="hp-trust-person hp-trust-link">
          <Image src={scottImg} alt="Scott Murray" class="hp-trust-avatar" width={48} height={48} format="webp" loading="eager" />
          <div class="hp-trust-person-info">
            <div class="hp-trust-person-stats">
              <div class="hp-trust-stat">
                <span class="hp-trust-number">2003</span>
                <span class="hp-trust-label">First Trip</span>
              </div>
              <div class="hp-trust-stat">
                <span class="hp-trust-number">20+</span>
                <span class="hp-trust-label">Return Trips</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="hp-trust-quote">"My first trip changed my life."</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/about/jenice/" class="hp-trust-person hp-trust-link">
          <Image src={jeniceImg} alt="Jenice Murray" class="hp-trust-avatar" width={48} height={48} format="webp" loading="eager" />
          <div class="hp-trust-person-info">
            <div class="hp-trust-person-stats">
              <div class="hp-trust-stat">
                <span class="hp-trust-number">Filipina</span>
                <span class="hp-trust-label">Raised in Pampanga</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="hp-trust-quote">"My home is where my heart is, and it is called the Philippines. <em>Tuloy po kayo</em> ‚Äî welcome!"</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       PLAN YOUR ROUTE ‚Äî Interactive Philippines map
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="hp-immersive-header">
    <div class="hp-immersive-gradient" style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #091e2f 0%, #0c3547 35%, #0D7377 65%, #091e2f 100%);" />
    <div class="hp-immersive-content">
      <h2 class="hp-immersive-title">Plan Your Route</h2>
      <p class="hp-immersive-text">Click any island to explore. Use our AI trip planner to build a custom itinerary with real prices, transport options, and local tips.</p>
      <a href="/plan/" class="hp-btn hp-btn--primary hp-btn--header">Plan Your Trip with AI &#10141;</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="hp-map" id="map">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="hp-map-layout">

        <!-- PHILIPPINES MAP -->
        <div class="hp-map-container" id="hpMapContainer">
          <div class="hp-map-tooltip" id="hpMapTooltip">
            <div class="hp-map-tooltip-name" id="hpTooltipName"></div>
            <div class="hp-map-tooltip-region" id="hpTooltipRegion"></div>
            <div class="hp-map-tooltip-status" id="hpTooltipStatus"></div>
          </div>
          <div id="hpLeafletMap"></div>
          <div class="hp-map-legend">
            <div class="hp-map-legend-item"><div class="hp-map-legend-dot hp-has-video"></div>Guide available</div>
            <div class="hp-map-legend-item"><div class="hp-map-legend-dot hp-coming-soon"></div>Coming soon</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- REGION CARDS -->
        <div class="hp-region-cards">
          <div class="hp-region-card" data-region="luzon">
            <div class="hp-region-card-header"><div class="hp-region-card-name">Luzon</div><div class="hp-region-card-count">23 destinations</div></div>
            <p class="hp-region-card-desc">The main island. Skip Manila, fly into Clark. Mountains in the north, surfing in the east, history everywhere.</p>
            <div class="hp-region-tags">
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/clark/">Clark</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/manila/">Manila</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/laoag/">Laoag</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/vigan/">Vigan</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/sagada/">Sagada</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/legazpi/">Legazpi</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/donsol/">Donsol</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/tagaytay/">Tagaytay</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/baguio/">Baguio</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/baler/">Baler</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/banaue/">Banaue</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/bataan/">Bataan</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/batanes/">Batanes</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/batangas/">Batangas</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/caramoan/">Caramoan</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/laguna/">Laguna</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/la-union/">La Union</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/marinduque/">Marinduque</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/mt-pulag/">Mt. Pulag</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/pagudpud/">Pagudpud</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/puerto-galera/">Puerto Galera</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/subic/">Subic</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/zambales/">Zambales</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hp-region-card" data-region="visayas">
            <div class="hp-region-card-header"><div class="hp-region-card-name">Visayas</div><div class="hp-region-card-count">13 destinations</div></div>
            <p class="hp-region-card-desc">Island-hopping paradise. Heart of Philippine beach culture with best diving, waterfalls, and mystical islands.</p>
            <div class="hp-region-tags">
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/cebu/">Cebu</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/bohol/">Bohol</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/siquijor/">Siquijor</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/dumaguete/">Dumaguete</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/boracay/">Boracay</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/iloilo/">Iloilo</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/bacolod/">Bacolod</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/malapascua/">Malapascua</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/guimaras/">Guimaras</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/sipalay/">Sipalay</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/biliran/">Biliran</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/samar/">Samar</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/tacloban/">Tacloban</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hp-region-card" data-region="palawan">
            <div class="hp-region-card-header"><div class="hp-region-card-name">Palawan</div><div class="hp-region-card-count">4 destinations</div></div>
            <p class="hp-region-card-desc">The Last Frontier. Dramatic limestone cliffs, hidden lagoons, clearest water on the planet.</p>
            <div class="hp-region-tags">
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/el-nido/">El Nido</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/coron/">Coron</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/puerto-princesa/">Puerto Princesa</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip" href="/destinations/cuyo/">Cuyo</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hp-region-card" data-region="mindanao">
            <div class="hp-region-card-header"><div class="hp-region-card-name">Mindanao</div><div class="hp-region-card-count">3 destinations</div></div>
            <p class="hp-region-card-desc">The road less traveled. World-class surfing in Siargao, volcanic islands in Camiguin, Davao's durian country.</p>
            <div class="hp-region-tags">
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/siargao/">Siargao</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/davao/">Davao</a>
              <a class="hp-dest-chip hp-chip-video" href="/destinations/camiguin/">Camiguin</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hp-map-cta">
        <a href="/plan/" class="hp-btn hp-btn--primary">Plan Your Trip with AI &#10141;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       IN-DEPTH GUIDES ‚Äî Destination grid
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="hp-immersive-header">
    <div class="hp-immersive-gradient" style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #064E3B 0%, #0D7377 35%, #0E7490 65%, #1A2332 100%);" />
    <div class="hp-immersive-content">
      <h2 class="hp-immersive-title">In-Depth Guides</h2>
      <p class="hp-immersive-text">Every price verified. Every restaurant visited. Every tip from personal experience.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="hp-destinations reveal">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="hp-dest-grid">
        {featuredSlugs.map((slug) => {
          const dest = allDests.find(d => d.slug === slug || d.id === slug);
          if (!dest) return null;
          const { title, tagline, region, budgetPerDay } = dest.data;
          const gradientVar = `var(--gradient-${title.toLowerCase()}, var(--gradient-homepage))`;
          const videoSrc = videoMap[slug] || '';
          const posterSrc = videoSrc ? videoSrc.replace('/destinations/', '/destinations/posters/').replace('.mp4', '.jpg') : '';
          return (
            <a href={`/destinations/${dest.slug || dest.id}/`} class="hp-dest-card">
              <div class="hp-dest-card-bg" style={`background: ${gradientVar};`}>
                {videoSrc && (
                  <video class="hp-dest-card-video" muted loop playsinline preload="none" poster={posterSrc} data-src={videoSrc}>
                  </video>
                )}
              </div>
              <div class="hp-dest-card-body">
                <span class="hp-dest-card-region">{region}</span>
                <h3 class="hp-dest-card-title">{title}</h3>
                {tagline && <p class="hp-dest-card-tagline">{tagline}</p>}
                {budgetPerDay && (
                  <p class="hp-dest-card-budget">From ${budgetPerDay.backpacker}/day</p>
                )}
              </div>
            </a>
          );
        })}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       LATEST FROM THE BLOG
       ============================================================ -->
  {latestPosts.length > 0 && (
    <section class="hp-immersive-header">
      <div class="hp-immersive-gradient" style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1A2332 0%, #2C5F2D 35%, #0D7377 65%, #1A2332 100%);" />
      <div class="hp-immersive-content">
        <h2 class="hp-immersive-title">Latest from the Blog</h2>
        <p class="hp-immersive-text">Stories, tips, and travel memories from 23 years of Philippines adventures.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="hp-blog reveal">
      <div class="container-content">
        <div class="hp-blog-grid">
          {latestPosts.map((post) => (
            <a class="hp-blog-card" href={`/blog/${post.slug || post.id}/`}>
              <div class="hp-blog-card-img" style={`background: var(--gradient-homepage);`}>
                {post.data.heroVideo && (
                  <video class="hp-blog-card-video" muted loop playsinline preload="none" data-src={post.data.heroVideo}></video>
                )}
                {post.data.heroImage && !post.data.heroVideo && (
                  <img src={post.data.heroImage} alt={post.data.title} loading="lazy" />
                )}
                {post.data.category && (
                  <span class="hp-blog-card-category">{post.data.category}</span>
                )}
              </div>
              <div class="hp-blog-card-body">
                <h3 class="hp-blog-card-title">{post.data.title}</h3>
                <p class="hp-blog-card-desc">{post.data.description}</p>
                <div class="hp-blog-card-meta">
                  <span>{post.data.author || 'Scott'}</span>
                  <span>&middot;</span>
                  <span>{new Date(post.data.pubDate).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'short', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric', timeZone: 'UTC' })}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
        <div class="hp-blog-cta">
          <a href="/blog/" class="hp-blog-cta-link">View All Posts &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  )}

  <!-- ============================================================
       WHAT MAKES THIS DIFFERENT ‚Äî Proof cards
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="hp-immersive-header">
    <div class="hp-immersive-gradient" style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1A2332 0%, #2d3748 35%, #1a3a3c 65%, #1A2332 100%);" />
    <div class="hp-immersive-content">
      <h2 class="hp-immersive-title">What Makes This Different</h2>
      <p class="hp-immersive-text">No press trips. No sponsored stays. Just two decades of personal experience.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="hp-proof reveal">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="hp-proof-grid">
        <div class="hp-proof-card">
          <h3 class="hp-proof-headline">Real Prices</h3>
          <p class="hp-proof-subhead">"Every price is one we paid"</p>
          <p class="hp-proof-detail">&#8369;150 sisig at Aling Lucing's. &#8369;1,700/day car rental in Clark. We verify every number on-site.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-proof-card">
          <h3 class="hp-proof-headline">Family Connections</h3>
          <p class="hp-proof-subhead">"Jenice grew up 15 minutes from Clark"</p>
          <p class="hp-proof-detail">Her brothers, her mom's birthday lechon, the Korean BBQ her family loves. This isn't research ‚Äî it's lived experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hp-proof-card">
          <h3 class="hp-proof-headline">No Sponsored Content</h3>
          <p class="hp-proof-subhead">"We don't take press trips"</p>
          <p class="hp-proof-detail">No hotel comps, no tourism board deals. We pay full price and tell you what we actually think.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       YOUR GUIDES ‚Äî Scott & Jenice (E-E-A-T)
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="hp-immersive-header">
    <div class="hp-immersive-gradient" style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0E4D5C 0%, #0D7377 40%, #14B8A6 70%, #064E3B 100%);" />
    <div class="hp-immersive-content">
      <h2 class="hp-immersive-title">Your Guides</h2>
      <p class="hp-immersive-text">An American travel planner and his Kapampangan wife ‚Äî 23 years, 20+ trips, and a toddler who's already island-hopping.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

